description: Displays the notebook files for the specified workgroup in paginated format.

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: Search filter string. Name (string) --- The name of the notebook to search for.

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: The name of the notebook to search for.

parameters.name: WorkGroup
parameters.description: The name of the Spark enabled workgroup to retrieve notebook metadata for.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A token generated by the Athena service that specifies where to continue pagination if a previous request was truncated. To obtain the next set of pages, pass in the NextToken from the response object of the previous page call.

nested_items.name: NotebookMetadataList
nested_items.description: The list of notebook metadata for the specified workgroup.

nested_items.name: WorkGroup
nested_items.description: The name of the Spark enabled workgroup to which the notebook belongs.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The time when the notebook was created.

nested_items.name: Type
nested_items.description: The type of notebook. Currently, the only valid type is IPYNB.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The time when the notebook was last modified.
